  "title": "Marketing Executive",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Responsible for end-to-end concept, market positioning and campaign planning for products and solutions</p></li><li><p>Coordinate all marketing events and exhibitions</p></li><li><p>Lead and manage creation of digital content such as videos, blogs, articles etc.</p></li><li><p>Facilitate and support marketing campaigns with relevant material and communications</p></li><li><p>Communicate internally and externally through various print and media avenues</p></li><li><p>Conduct market data research and analysis</p></li><li><p>Lead search engine optimization and associated projects<br /></p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Diploma or Degree in Chemical or Environmental Engineering, or equivalent <br /></p></li></ul><p><strong>HOW TO APPLY:</strong></p><p>Interested applicants, kindly send your resume in MS WORD format or please click on “Apply Now”.</p><p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p>Important Note: Trust Recruit Pte Ltd is committed to safeguarding your personal data in accordance with the Personal Data Protection Act (PDPA).</p><p>Please read our privacy statement on our corporate website.</p><p>Trust Recruit Pte Ltd</p><p>EA License No: 19C9950</p><p>EA Personnel: Tan Sin Yong (Stella)</p><p>EA Personnel Reg No: R24124127</p>",
